snippet.textDisplay: Its a beautiful song , sung by Nabeel and sung majestically. Let me tell who so ever read this; did any one realised that the crisp of song is, whatever is the circumstances you are facing, you will never forget the person whom you fell in love with. It's my experience . Let me tell you a story. Once the there was a boy who tried this whole life to be single. Suddenly one day a girl came and proposed him. He was astonished. Not 'cos some random girl proposed him, but a girl who was so demanding, beautiful and genuinely great hearted. After having all great time for 2 years , she left him (still alive) but gone from his life. Now it's been more than 3 years that he didn't have any contact with her but he still remember her & want her back in his life  and that too Bewajah...
